Maurice Kaufmann https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maurice_Kaufmann 0 Maurice Harington Kaufmann (29 June 1927 – 21 September 1997) was a British actor of stage, film and television, who specialised in whodunits and horror films, from 1954 to 1981, when he retired.
